Native compilation:

1) sudo apt-get  update
2) sudo apt-get install libncurses-dev flex bison openssl libssl-dev dkms libelf-dev libudev-dev libpci-dev libiberty-dev autoconf
3) download the kernel source code from https://www.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v3.x
4) tar -xvf linux-3.19.8.tar.gz
5) cd linux-3.19.8/
6) make menuconfig
7) make
8) make modules
9) make modules_install
10) make install
11) reboot
